million notional, the Goldman salesperson quoted:
For Tomorrow=E2=80=99s strike: 3mL+50 bid (PTMM +53)for TODAY=E2=80=99s str=
ike: 3mL+100
When the client responded with interest in the T+1 strike, the Goldman sale=
