Here is the (new)  bankruptcy docket, and here is the =E2=80=9CDebtor=E2=80=
=99s Statement Regarding Refiling of Chapter 11 Case=E2=80=9D explaining wh=
y J&J thinks this time will be different. The simple version of it is that =
there is no longer a=C2=A0Funding Agreement in which J&J =E2=80=94=C2=A0the=
