issed. =E2=80=A6=C2=A0Under the new financing arrangements, J&J=E2=80=99s s=
upport is only available in bankruptcy and only if approved by this Court. =
=E2=80=A6 As a result, J&J=E2=80=99s balance sheet and liquidity were no lo=
nger available to the Debtor before the filing of this second chapter 11 ca=
